    <title>java基础第二天</title>
    <url>/2026/03/07/java_base/java%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%A9/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、运算符"><a href="#一、运算符" class="headerlink" title="一、运算符"></a>一、运算符</h1><h2 id="1、“-”符号在java中的特殊用途"><a href="#1、“-”符号在java中的特殊用途" class="headerlink" title="1、“+”符号在java中的特殊用途"></a>1、“+”符号在java中的特殊用途</h2><p>“+”符号与字符串运算的时候用作连接符的，其结果依然是一个字符串</p>
<p>“+”号运算时从左往右算，能计算则计算，计算不了才连接。例如：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int a = 5;</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(&quot;hello&quot; + a + &#x27;a&#x27;);</span><br><span class="line">//结果为hello5a</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(a + &#x27;a&#x27; + &quot;hello&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">//结果为102hello</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="2、逻辑运算符"><a href="#2、逻辑运算符" class="headerlink" title="2、逻辑运算符"></a>2、逻辑运算符</h2><p>逻辑与：&amp;<br>逻辑或：|<br>逻辑非：！<br>逻辑异或：^</p>
<p>短路与：&amp;&amp;  （判断结果与“&amp;”一样，过程不同：左边为false，右边则不执行）<br>短路或：||  （判断结果与“|”一样，过程不同：左边为true，右边则不执行）</p>
<h1 id="二、身体健康指数计算"><a href="#二、身体健康指数计算" class="headerlink" title="二、身体健康指数计算"></a>二、身体健康指数计算</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">package BMI_and_BMR;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">import java.util.Scanner;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//身体健康指数计算方法</span><br><span class="line">public class BMI_and_BMR &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Scanner human_data = new Scanner(System.in);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(&quot;请输入您的身高：&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        double human_height = human_data.nextDouble();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(&quot;请输入您的体重：&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        double human_weight = human_data.nextDouble();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(&quot;请输入您的性别：&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        String human_sex = human_data.next();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(&quot;请输入您的年龄：&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        int human_age = human_data.nextInt();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        double human_BMI = getBMI(human_height,human_weight);</span><br><span class="line">        double human_BMR = getBMR(human_height,human_weight,human_sex,human_age);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(&quot;您的BMI指数为：&quot; + human_BMI);</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(&quot;您的BMR指数为：&quot; + human_BMR);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        if(gethealthy(human_BMI,human_BMR,human_sex))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            System.out.println(&quot;您很健康&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            System.out.println(&quot;您不太健康&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    //BMI计算</span><br><span class="line">    public static double getBMI(double height, double weight) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        return weight / (height * height);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    //BMR计算</span><br><span class="line">    public static double getBMR(double height, double weight, String sex, int age)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        return (&quot;男&quot;.equals(sex) ? (13.397 * weight) + (4.799 * height) - (5.677 * age) + 88.362 : (9.247 * weight) + (3.098 * height) - (4.330 * age) + 447.593);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    //健康判断</span><br><span class="line">    public static boolean gethealthy(double BMI, double BMR, String sex)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        return &quot;男&quot;.equals(sex) ? (BMI &gt; 18.5 &amp;&amp; BMI &lt; 24.9) &amp;&amp; BMR &gt; 1500 &amp;&amp; BMR &lt; 2500 : (BMI &gt; 18.5 &amp;&amp; BMI &lt; 24.9) &amp;&amp; BMR &gt; 1200 &amp;&amp; BMR &lt; 2000;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="三、程序流程控制"><a href="#三、程序流程控制" class="headerlink" title="三、程序流程控制"></a>三、程序流程控制</h1><h2 id="1、switch分支结构的注意事项"><a href="#1、switch分支结构的注意事项" class="headerlink" title="1、switch分支结构的注意事项"></a>1、switch分支结构的注意事项</h2><p>表达式类型只能是byte、short、int、char，JDK5开始支持枚举，JDK7开始支持String，不支持double、float、long</p>
<p>case给出的值不允许重复，且只能是字面量，不能是变量</p>
<p>正常使用switch的时候，不要忘记写break，否则会出现穿透现象（匹配到一个case执行完之后执行下一个case，直到遇到break或超出switch范围）</p>
<p>多个case块如果程序内容相同，可以利用穿透现象减少书写代码</p>
<h1 id="四、计算器"><a href="#四、计算器" class="headerlink" title="四、计算器"></a>四、计算器</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">package calculator;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">import java.util.InputMismatchException;</span><br><span class="line">import java.util.Scanner;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//计算器程序可以加减乘除</span><br><span class="line">public class calculator &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        while(true)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            try&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                System.out.println(&quot;两位大爷里边儿请~，当前可供挑选美人儿：（+、-、*、/）&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">                Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);</span><br><span class="line">                double num1 = sc.nextDouble();</span><br><span class="line">                String oprt = sc.next();</span><br><span class="line">                double num2 = sc.nextDouble();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                switch(oprt)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    case &quot;+&quot; :</span><br><span class="line">                        System.out.println(num1 + &quot;+&quot; + num2 + &quot;=&quot; + (num1 + num2));</span><br><span class="line">                        break;</span><br><span class="line">                    case &quot;-&quot; :</span><br><span class="line">                        System.out.println(num1 + &quot;-&quot; + num2 + &quot;=&quot; + (num1 - num2));</span><br><span class="line">                        break;</span><br><span class="line">                    case &quot;*&quot; :</span><br><span class="line">                        System.out.println(num1 + &quot;+&quot; + num2 + &quot;=&quot; + (num1 * num2));</span><br><span class="line">                        break;</span><br><span class="line">                    case &quot;/&quot; :</span><br><span class="line">                        if(num2 == 0)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                            System.out.println(&quot;除0错误,二大爷可没钱哦！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">                            break;</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                            System.out.println(num1 + &quot;+&quot; + num2 + &quot;=&quot; + (num1 / num2));</span><br><span class="line">                            break;</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    default :</span><br><span class="line">                        System.out.println(&quot;运算符不合法，其他美人在忙！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">                        break;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                System.out.println(&quot;\n&quot;.repeat(2));</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;catch(InputMismatchException e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                System.out.println(&quot;输入格式错误，这不合规矩~！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="五、猜数字"><a href="#五、猜数字" class="headerlink" title="五、猜数字"></a>五、猜数字</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">package guess_num;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">import java.util.InputMismatchException;</span><br><span class="line">import java.util.Scanner;</span><br><span class="line">import java.util.Random;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">public class guess_num &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(&quot;来玩猜数字游戏吧，1~100之间的整数哦！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        //随机生成1~100数字</span><br><span class="line">        Random random = new Random();</span><br><span class="line">        int answer = random.nextInt(100) + 1;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        while(true)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            try&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                int guess = sc.nextInt();</span><br><span class="line">                if(guess == answer)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    System.out.println(&quot;猜对了！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">                    break;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;else if(guess &lt; 1 || guess &gt; 100)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    System.out.println(&quot;答案在1~100中哦！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;else if(guess &gt; answer)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    System.out.println(&quot;猜大了！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    System.out.println(&quot;猜小了！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;catch(InputMismatchException e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                System.out.println(&quot;这是1~100的猜整数游戏哦！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                //清除缓冲区内容，便于下次输入</span><br><span class="line">                String clear_guess = sc.nextLine();</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="六、验证码"><a href="#六、验证码" class="headerlink" title="六、验证码"></a>六、验证码</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">package verification_code;</span><br><span class="line">import java.util.InputMismatchException;</span><br><span class="line">import java.util.Scanner;</span><br><span class="line">import java.util.Random;</span><br><span class="line">public class verification_code &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);</span><br><span class="line">        Random r = new Random();</span><br><span class="line">        String v_code = &quot;&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(&quot;请设置验证码长度：&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        while(true)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            try&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                //输入想要的验证码位数</span><br><span class="line">                int len = sc.nextInt();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                for(int i = 0;i &lt; len;++i)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    int random = -1;</span><br><span class="line">                    while(true)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        //0~122包含了所有大小写字母和自然数的ascii码</span><br><span class="line">                        random = r.nextInt(123);</span><br><span class="line">                        if((random &gt;= &#x27;0&#x27; &amp;&amp; random &lt;= &#x27;9&#x27;) || (random &gt;= &#x27;A&#x27; &amp;&amp; random &lt;= &#x27;Z&#x27;) || (random &gt;= &#x27;a&#x27; &amp;&amp; random &lt;= &#x27;z&#x27;))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                            break;</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    v_code += (char)random;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                System.out.println(v_code);</span><br><span class="line">                break;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;catch(InputMismatchException e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                System.out.println(&quot;请输入有效整数：&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">                String clear_len = sc.nextLine();</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="七、找素数"><a href="#七、找素数" class="headerlink" title="七、找素数"></a>七、找素数</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">package find_prime_num;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//输出101~200素数</span><br><span class="line">public class find_prime_num &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        boolean isprime = true;</span><br><span class="line">        int count = 0;</span><br><span class="line">        for(int i = 101;i &lt;= 200;++i)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            isprime = true;</span><br><span class="line">            for(int j = 2;j &lt;= Math.sqrt(i);++j)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                if(i % j == 0)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    isprime = false;</span><br><span class="line">                    break;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            if(isprime)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                ++count;</span><br><span class="line">                System.out.print(i + &quot; &quot;);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println();</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(&quot;101~200中素数总共个数：&quot; + count);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
